{
  "title": "Romantic Spicy Jamaican Tarragon Bake",
  "description": "A lacto-vegetarian-friendly, spicy bake featuring the unique flavors of Jamaican cuisine and the romance of tarragon. Perfect for a dinner date or special occasion.",
